## Overview
This directory contains the official Standard Operating Procedure governing the execution of the month-end close.

The objective is to ensure reporting is:

- accurate  
- complete  
- timely  
- repeatable  
- audit defensible  

The close process is the backbone of financial control.

---

## What This SOP Covers
The procedure establishes mandatory governance for:

- Roles and responsibilities  
- Status progression  
- Risk visibility  
- Evidence requirements  
- Treatment of estimates  
- Dependency management  
- Post-close discipline  
- Version control  

It applies to **all entities and reporting periods**.

